data.description: Dream Home! Better than new construction with 4 BEDS and a 4 CAR GARAGE is ready for you!. New kitchen updates with professionally finished cabinets includes a walk-in pantry. The main floor boasts NEW LVP FLOORING. This home is truly move-in ready. It is one of the largest floor plans in Hidden Valley Farm 4 bedrooms + a study. The owners suite is grand at 18 x 16 with a 11 x 6 seating nook, it includes a 2 sided fireplace and 5 piece owners bath. Property is amazingly landscaped on one of the largest lots available and a 834sf - 4 Car Garage! Check out the Weld RE-4 school district on Facebook or weldre4.org! Range View Elementary, Severance Middle School and Severance High School.
